snippet.title: 丹回廊～アカイカイロウ～　AKAI Corridor - If you proceed to the 8th floor, your soul will be saved, probably!
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://gotchagotchagames.itch.io/akaikairou?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt The first floor is normal.

Please turn right when the floor is normal, and turn left when there is an abnormality.

If you proceed to the 8th floor, your soul will be saved, probably.
